title: Lasante - Seychelles Coronavirus Tool
description: *Important: This app only works in Seychelles* A free app to help you understand what to do next about Coronavirus (COVID-19) in the Seychelles. ✅Unlimited virtual COVID-19 screening ✅Personalised guidance on what to do next ✅Direct call access to 141 national helpline ✅Access to live Seychelles case statistics ✅Push notifications for new cases
